      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/15b6937c-a68e-11e3-8a3e-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  No failures.",
