      "date": "2014-03-08 08:52:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5cda1668-a696-11e3-aad0-52540035b04c).  Ran 10 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-rsync-test.",
